{"tid":2290583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《全民造星III》參賽者劉若寶Polly瘋狂走音照入圍，賽果被質疑","createTime":"2020-11-18T06:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T16:30:16.000Z","uid":38539,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c61796c56a1e77b1a7871ddaa8efdcba43701d4a","tid":2290583,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uBjKk100ETE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuBjKk100ETE&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1cbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=b560a620\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uBjKk100ETE</a><br />\n<br />\nViuTV《全民造星III》昨晚播出第12集，其中一名本身不懂唱歌及跳舞的參賽者，31歲劉若寶（Polly），在唱歌時更難得一見全程走音，但3位評審竟然皆給予藍燈入圍，郭偉亮問Polly：「好難由頭到尾個key係唔啱，成首唱晒，逆境嘅時候佢都可以喺台上繼續表演，我覺得佢領略到the show must go on，所以畀燈佢。」Polly卻指自己不知走音，卓韻芝取笑：「妳可以入女ERROR，你唔覺得自己走音、有問題，妳都癡線﹗」卓韻芝表示想多看Polly才畀燈，她說：「不過你3盞燈（入圍）啲人會好嬲，所以扣返你一盞燈。」Polly在賽前亦承認自己只靠樣入圍，她說：「都係一個優點嚟，如果我因為靚而俾我入，喺唱歌跳舞我會落多啲工夫。」<br />\n<br />\n其他參賽者則表示，五音不全的Polly得到3盞燈入圍，是對所有參賽者不尊重，亦有參賽者退出節目抗議。此外，同場還有大跳「折骨舞」的參賽者趙祥成（Ben），其奪目演出大獲好評而入圍，有指他是香港數一數二的「折骨舞」達人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201118/JX242ZCCYBFFZIYYH7HTUYUTPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201118%2FJX242ZCCYBFFZIYYH7HTUYUTPU%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1cbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=7bb3df3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201118%2FJX242ZCCYBFFZIYYH7HTUYUTPU%2F&h=a77cd8a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201118/JX242ZCCYBFFZIYYH7HTUYUTPU/</a>"},{"pid":"1a79e760a97c14c07c078a7e580edc09d03c2f26","tid":2290583,"uid":38539,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:13:11.000Z","msg":"唱到咁，笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6